              "path": ["availability", "student", "next"]
            },
            "description": "hasRole('SERVICE') only - normally called by session-service, never by a real user. The pre-request script mints a throwaway SERVICE token so this can be exercised directly. Returns 404 if no student is AVAILABLE."
          },
          "event": [
